response.overview: Wubbzy's a lovable critter who lives in a wonderful place called Wuzzleburg. Bouncing along on his spring-like tail, he and his friends, Widget and Walden, wind up in all sorts of wild adventures. Created for preschoolers, WOW! WOW! WUBBZY is a fun program that also teaches some important lessons. And while W's predominate in Wubbzy's wonderland, the alliterative gang learn how to embrace their inner "Arrr" in PIRATE TREASURE as they scour the beach for sunken booty, wander the city grid of Plaidsville, and much more.
response.title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: Pirate Treasure
